  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Gharak Squint-Eye</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Jhattar\" title=\"Jhattar\">Jhattar</a></i></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Jogos_Nhai\" title=\"Jogos Nhai\">Jogos Nhai</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Plains_of_the_Jogos_Nhai\" title=\"Plains of the Jogos Nhai\">Plains of the Jogos Nhai</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Gharak Squint-Eye</b> was a <i><a href=\"/index.php/Jhattar\" title=\"Jhattar\">jhattar</a></i> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Jogos_Nhai\" title=\"Jogos Nhai\">Jogos Nhai</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gharak_Squint-Eye&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to legend Gharak slew the last of the <a href=\"/index.php/Jhogwin\" title=\"Jhogwin\">Jhogwin</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_in_the_Howling_Hills\" title=\"Battle in the Howling Hills\">Battle in the Howling Hills</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf842_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf842-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span clas